To make it even easier for you to operate the Pirate Chain wallets, we have created a new easy wallet installation script. This works for Pirate wallets (Windows) and offers: 


- Fast block syncing
- Bootstrap downloading
- Bootstrap extract
- Zcash parameters installation
- Auto-launch of wallet


How To Use The Script:

-Download Wget64.exe
-Download The wallet bat file  (ex. Sevenseas.bat)
-Open Wallet bat file (ex. Sevenseas.bat)


What The Script Does:

-Wallet Downloading
-Fast block syncing 
-Bootstrap downloading
-Bootstrap extract
-Zcash parameters installation
-Auto-launch of wallet

Video Tutorial https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H0XtWv4Zohk
